data.description:
Nestled in a tranquil cul-de-sac, this home presents a blend of elegance and functionality. A charming brick paver driveway and a private front porch welcome you. Inside, high ceilings and an open floor plan create a spacious and inviting ambiance.
The heart of this home is the kitchen, featuring a generous island, stainless steel appliances, and elegant granite countertops. A walk-in pantry adds convenience to your culinary adventures. Upstairs, a versatile loft stands ready for your personal touch. Outside, a large covered patio is great for dining and relaxation. The private pool, complete with a soothing water feature, provides a serene escape right in your own backyard.  With a tranquil location and modern luxuries, this home epitomizes both style and convenience.
